## Transfer Money [/accounts/transfer]

### Transfer between two Accounts [POST]

    Model (application/json)

    {
        "date": "2020-03-25",
        "from_account_id": 7,
        "to_account_id": 105,
        "amount": "200",
        "particulars": "cash transfer"
    }

+ Request (application/json)
+ Response 201 (application/json)

